=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_OneZero_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with complex oscillator character around 52 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with highpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 51.7632
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.0279
  harmonic_regularity: 0.1267
  pitch_clarity: 14.7374
  inharmonicity: 0.0399
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: 0.6407
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: OneZero Example 2
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/OneZero.html
